tasks.description:
Append underwriting-service database variables to infra/.env.example under a labelled comment block:

# Underwriting Service
UNDERWRITING_DB_NAME=loanflow_underwriting_db

The shared DATABASE_HOST, DATABASE_PORT, DATABASE_USER, DATABASE_PASSWORD, and MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD variables are reused from the base MySQL block.

Also update infra/mysql/init/01_init.sql to provision the underwriting database:
CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS loanflow_underwriting_db CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON loanflow_underwriting_db.* TO '${DATABASE_USER}'@'%';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
